[Monday 9-30-19]: My next Super Mario Maker 2 level is up. It's called "Athletic Sky Jumps!" The code to play it is: GLS-Y0B-BQG "Man! It feels so good to finally release/upload this level. I have been working on it since July. It is platform goodness of the 90s with somewhat of the new autoscroll mechanics which flows surprisingly smooth. My favorite parts of this level is the entire subcourse area. The gameplay and visually....'Oh-la-la. Pretty.' Heh heh. Okay. I'll stop being weird. Enjoy the dem sky jumps.  If you have stages  you want me to play post them in the comments below or in my other SMM2 post. Thanks a bunch! Children Of Morta es un juego desarrollado por Dead Mage que ya está disponible en early access y espera a su lanzamiento en consolas a partir del 15 de octubre. Esta entrega es un juego de RPG de acción que cuenta la historia de una familia de héroes a la cual controlaremos a través de un mundo generado de manera procedural. Tanto su estética pixel art como su jugabilidad son sus alegatos principales. Primero Contamos con un juego que trae unas animaciones extraordinarias y luego un sistema de progresión muy bien trabajado el cual se extiende hasta seis personajes que en conjunto con el combate que es divertido y equilibrado hacen de éste un juego muy entretenido.  #childrenofmorta #deadmage #indie #game #gamer #gaming #videogame #videojuego #ps4 #playstation #nintendo #nintendoswitch #switch #xboxone #xbox #microsoft #pc #pcgaming #pcgamer #pcgame #roguelike #mazmorras #mazmorra

When your powers combine  you become... a Share Post! Yup  that's right  both the Share Post and Challenge Post have now been combined into one. Makes posting a lot easier (and moderating as well as reading can be very hard for some people 😑). - So  whatever course you made  you can post it below. However  the rules have not changed. Your comment must include the following: *Course ID *Type of course (puzzle  normal  fun  platforming  kaizo  speedrun  troll  etc) *Estimated difficulty level (easy  normal  hard  expert etc)  If you post an incomplete comment it will be deleted without warning. 🤷‍♂️ - Happy sharing! - #supermario #supermariomaker #supermariomaker2 #mariomaker #nintendo #nintendoswitch #switchlite #videogames #games #gaming #gamer #create #share #play #enjoy #fun #mm2c #challenge #courseid #sharelevels #sharing

Trine 4 se prepara para su llegada a las tiendas el 08 de Octubre y estará disponible para PlayStation 4  Xbox One  Nintendo Switch y PC. Estamos frente a una nueva entrega de esta saga desarrollada por Frozenbyte. En la que volvemos a encarnar a Amadeus  Poncio y Soya a través de sus aventuras por un mundo lleno de plataformas y puzzles que completar. Para los amantes de este tipo de juegos de corte clásico con una cámara de scroll lateral hay buenas noticias por que la saga vuelve a sus inicios y deja atrás el fallido pero valiente intento de llevar el juego a las 3D en la entrega pasada.  #trine #trine4 #frozenbyte #indie #nintendoswitch #nintendo #switch #ps4 #playstation #xbox #xboxone #microsoft #pc #pcgaming #pcgamer #pcgame #game #gaming #gamer #videogame #videojuego #2d #plataformas #aventuras #puzzle

Favourite Grand Prix track from the first three 🏆? For me it’s a really close tie between Twilight Tour and Prehistoric Playground but I prefer Twlight Tour as it feels real smooth to drive on plus the aesthetic and visual design is really good  Spyro Circuit is in last place for me. Beenox did a really good job with the visuals and aesthetics (I like how there’s gems and baskets instead)  but it feels really cramped to drive on plus you’re just going straight most of the time  What’s your rankings mine are 1. Twilight Tour 2. Prehistoric Playground 3. Spyro Circuit  Can’t wait for Nina’s Nightride  I have a feeling that’s gonna be on the same quality as the first two ___  #ctr #ps4 #xboxone #nintendoswitch #crashteamracing #ctrnf #crashbandicoot #crashteamracingnitrofueled

Per quanto possa essere un nuovo soulslike  Code Vein si conferma come un prodotto dall’anima originale e complessa  sfruttando l’estetica giapponese per proporre una delle esperienze più divertenti del genere. Attraverso a un sistema tanto accessibile quanto profondo e malleabile  vivere i panni di un Redivivo diventa una sfida più che gustosa che può essere adattata a qualsiasi tipo di giocatore. Ma il combattimento non è l’unico elemento invitante del gioco: la trama coinvolgente – anche grazie a un editor più che ottimo – e il ricco cast sono solo la portata principale di un mondo fatto di misteri  ricordi e colpi di scena sconvolgenti. Nonostante qualche comprensibile difetto  Bandai Namco e le menti dietro God Eater sono riusciti a produrre una nuova formula vincente  facendo nascere un’esperienza che si fa decisamente perdonare della lunga attesa.⠀ La mia Recensione di Code Vein per Game Division!⠀ -⠀ -⠀ #codevein #bandainamco #anime #vampire #soulslike #pc #ps4 #playstation #nintendoswitch #sony #xbox #mcirosoft #gamingfolk #gaming #gamer #game #videogame #videogames #videogioco #videogiochi #nerd #geek #singleplayer #multiplayer #player #playing #play #gamereview #recensione

Sırf bir iki seferle bıkanlar için değişik değişik pokemonlar  garip garip antrenörler. Gerek yok! Ver bize ashvari karakteri  misty'i  brock'u  bir de pikachu'yu tamam. Aynı o minvalde yapılmış bir oyun. Bu tarz bir oyun için oynama süresi de gayet doyurucu. . Oyunda en büyük değişiklik şeker sistemi ve pokemon yakalama sistemi olmuş  yakalamak için önceden canını azaltır sonra pokeball atardık  şimdi ise direk yakalama kısmına geçiyor  berry gibi yemlerle pokemonu sakinleştirip sonra yakalıyoruz. Yakaladığın fazla ya da istemediğin pokemonları Profesör Oak'a gönderirsen de sana şeker veriyor. Bununla pokemonların değişik özelliklerini geliştirebiliyorsun. . Zelda Link’s Awakening – это ремейк классической Зельды с видом сверху  выпущенной ещё в далёком 1993 году на #GameBoy. На #NintendoSwitch игра перенесена практически с учётом всех нюансов  с улучшением графики и управления. Эта забота одновременно и плюс и минус игры. Бывалые геймеры будут рады и вспомнят былые времена  когда каждый секрет в подобных РПГ решался далеко не сразу и приходилось пробегать всю карту в течении нескольких часов  чтобы наконец понять  что и куда дальше. Но сегодняшние геймеры скорее назовут это проблемой геймдизайна  но никак не фишкой игры.  Что касается меня  то проблемы при прохождении я испытал буквально пару тройку раз. И это не проблемы с загадками в подземельях (они то как раз здесь очень крутые и их интересно решать именно самому)  а практически всегда это был вопрос «Куда же идти дальше?» Порой игра даёт лишь мелкие подсказки  которые не всегда очевидны. Решал это с помощью гайда для версии игры 1993 года (благо вся карта перенесена в ремейк 1 в 1) и зазрения совести от этого не испытываю. Пробегать всю карту и рубить мечом каждый кустик в надежде  что вот сейчас то под этим будет секретный вход в нужное подземелье… время дороже и времена не те :) В целом  ремейк однозначно понравился. Особо хочется отметить графику и стилистику проекта. Эстетика пластиковых игрушек выглядит замечательно  мир и персонажи очаровывают. #LinksAwakening способна вернуть вас в детство  даже если вы не играли в оригинал. А #Switch получил ещё один отличный эксклюзив в свою библиотеку.  #zelda #nintendoswitchgames #nintendo #linkzelda #portablegaming #rpggames #videogames #consolegaming #консольныеигры #видеоигры #обзорыигр #games #gaminglife

Thought I'd share my current shelf situation  the lighting can be pretty poor in my place so I did what I could.  The first image is in my second bedroom with most of the collection  PS1  PS2  PSP  Vita  Gamecube  Wii  Wii U  DS  3DS and the Game Boy line. There's a few figures around as well as some rad gifts and sentimental things  I have plenty more of them but can't display them all. If you can see I have games from all over the globe  I don't really care what region a game comes from as long as I can play it in some fashion and it's physical. Instgram sure does compress the shit out of images though.  The second image is in my living area  PS4  PS3 and Switch  the collections I tend to give the most attention and play time currently. There's another 2 rows of PS3 cut off and the shelf next to it is my anime as well as movies and TV shows that my partner and I own. I was suprised the other day to see on my game collecting app that I hit 160 PS4 games... what a crazy console with so many games that are fantastic. Still many I need to play as I sure as hell haven't played eveything I own. Across all consoles  I'd say I've played somewhere between 80-85% of games  and finished another 80% of those. The rest  I got my time in and I'm satisfied. To want to finish everything is a fool's errand.  Also for those who may just think I'm messy  the games that are pulled put slightly are the ones I am yet to play  want to get back to or intend to replay.  #playstation #nintendo #ps1 #ps2 #ps3 #ps4 #psp #psvita #wii #wiiu #nintendoswitch #gamecube #nintendods #nintendo3ds #nintendogames #gameboy #gamecollection #gamersofaus #videogamecollection #shelfie

Salah satu game indie milik Xbox Game Studios telah dirilis untuk port Nintendo Switch  mengingat Nintendo dan Microsoft memiliki hubungan baik dalam bentuk kerja sama di dalam mengembangkan industri game dunia.  Salah satu hal unik yang di kemukakan oleh game director dari Ori and the Blind Forest Thomas Mahler  game ini malah lebih optimize untuk platform Switch  katanya mereka bisa memaksimalkan kinerja engine mereka di Switch dalam bentuk animasi 60 hertz  sedangkan di Xbox hanya mencapai 30 Hertz.  Yang artinya  game ini justru mala lebih optimize di Switch ketimbang di Xbox One sebagai induk game tersebut pada awalnya. 🎮 BARCODE BATTLERS II 時空を超えた戦士たち (Warriors who travelled in time) . Barcode Battlers was a series of Handheld consoles made by Epoch. . Barcode scanning toys and arcade games were extremely popular in the 90's Japan including the Datach Famicom add on  the later Digivices and Barcode Wars by Bandai. The strength of the Barcode Wars series was its connection to nintendo  allowing them to make exclusive barcode games with nintendo franchise such as Mario Bros and Zelda. . It also allowed players connect to their Super Famicom or original Gameboy via the 'Barcode Boy' to send data from the barcode cards into the Barcode Battler console games. . Barcode Battler was highly successful in Japan and even saw a release of western versions with alternative art and characters. . Did you go to the eshop and download yourself a copy of Gold Silver or Crystal?  Only getting the Red Gyradose as your first shiny? And want more?  What if i told you that in Gen 2 you can breed a shiny with a non shiny Pokemon Turning your odds from 1/8192 to 1/64 through breeding? --- Shiny hunting feels impossible through gen 2 and onward to some of us because of how high the odds are and theres no shiny charm till black and white 2.  Well In gen 2 theres something in the coding that makes Breeding a shiny with a mon shiny pop out shinies a bit faster  I believe its only breeding males with females of the same species or egg group  Anyway.  So you may not have a shiny ditto yet  Theres two ways to get one Random encounter one Or Use your red gyradose to trade to red blue or yellow use on a ditto only with mimic then catch and trade back to gsc  If you just have the Shiny Gyradose what can you breed with it?  One example is Dragonair  Another Tentacruel  A helpful thing to know is your egg groups  Gyradose is in the Water 2 and dragon egg group Dragonair is in the Dragon egg group Ekans is in the field and dragon egg group Tentacruel is in the water 2 egg group Ekans can breed with any field egg group mon such as mankey and primeape even eevee  I have done this shiny hunt method myself Getting myself various Shiny Pokemon  Since theres no abilities eggs will hatch relatively slow  Some hatch faster than others such as Magikarp hatching faster than lapras or snorlax  So my suggestion is trying magikarp first test your patience Then try Dratini or Something else.  If you're like "woah shit is this true?" 𝑷𝑹𝑰𝑪𝑬  14€ <=> 𝑪𝑬𝑵𝑨  1600𝒅𝒊𝒏  GTA V je akciona avantura u otvorenom svetu. Igra se odvija u fiktivnom  svetu San Andreas  a inspiracija je Južna Kalifornija. Igrač slobodno  može da se kreće po svetu kao i gradu Los Santosu (zamena za Los Angeles). Igra može da se igra iz prvog ili trećeg lica  a glavni junak  se kreće peške ili u vozilu. Glavni junak hara San Andreasom  a većina  misija uključuje pucanje i vožnju. Igrači koji prilikom igre čine zločin  iniciraće odgovarajuću reakciju pravosuđa. To će se meriti tzv. "wanted" sistemom. Dodatak igri je multiplejer mod GTA Online koji daje  mogućnost da se do 30 igrača uključi u kooperativne ili takmičarske  mečeve. Dugo iščekivana  GTA 5 je oborila sve rekorde po prodavanosti  širom sveta  a pokupila je i sve pohvale za dizajn igrača  otvorenog  sveta  kao i sam gameplay. Veći broj igračkih časopisa dodelio joj je  titulu "Igra godine". #psx #nba #nba2k20 #fifa #fifa20 #pes #pes2020 #crvenazvezda #partizan #playstation #playstation4 #game #gameshop #nfs #cup #liga #xbox #ps4 #ps4pro #nintendo #nintendoswitch #sega #instagram #new #newyork #losangeles #gta

Od prelaska sa parkura i jedinstvenim interakcijama sa okolinom  do novog borbenog i blockbuster akcione borbe  to je Spider-Man  za razliku od bilo kog koga ste prethodno igrali. Sony Interactive Entertainment  Insomniac Games i Marvel udružili su se kako bi stvorili potpuno novu i autentičnu avanturu Spider-Man. Ovo nije Spider-Man kog ste upoznali ili ste ikada videli. Ovo je iskusni Peter Parker koji je više majstorski izvežban u borbi protiv velikog kriminala u New Yorku. Istvremeno se nastoji uravnotežiti sa svojim haotičnim privatnim životom i karijerom dok se sudbina miliona njujorčana oslanja na njegova ramena.  #psx #nba #nba2k20 #fifa #fifa20 #pes #pes2020 #crvenazvezda #partizan #playstation #playstation4 #game #gameshop #nfs #cup #liga #xbox #ps4 #ps4pro #nintendo #nintendoswitch #sega #instagram #new #newyork #losangeles #speedrman

#MilanGamesWeek2019 🎮 Si è da poco conclusa l’edizione 2019 di #MilanGamesWeek. Un’edizione per certi versi un po’ “ridotta” rispetto agli ultimi anni  con poche anteprime ed esclusive da provare. A farla da padrone è stata @playstationit con un’area molto vasta e con due titoli molto interessanti da poter giocare in anteprima  #FinalFantasyVIIRemake e #MarvelsAvengers. Non da meno sono state @nintendoswitchitalia con la possibilità di provare #PokemonSpadaScudo e #LuigisMansion3  e @xboxitalia con la prova in anteprima di #GhostReconBreakpoint in collaborazione con @ubisoftitalia. Piccolo stand ma non meno importante quello di @bethesda_it che offriva l’anteprima di #DoomEternal. Per il resto poche altre novità e meno tornei di eSports rispetto allo scorso anno. Los Donkey Kong Country son mis plataformas favoritos. . Me enamoré de estos monos con DKC2 Diddy's Kong Quest en SNES que pude conocer gracias a un amigo con la consola ya que yo no tenía. Me parece el mejor de esa trilogía y me lo he pasado un montón de veces  sacando siempre que puedo el 102%. . Yo jugué a esta trilogía desordenada  porque el primer DKC fue el último que llegó a mis manos. Me gustó menos que los otros por eso  porque sus secuelas mejoraban la fórmula y se echaban cosas en falta en esta primera entrega al jugarla por primera vez después. . Me alegró mucho que Nintendo recuperara la saga en Wii  aunque compuse catar DKC Returns hasta que salió la versión 3D para Nintendo 3DS  la cual me volví a comprar (tras vender un primer modelo que tuve) por esté juegazo ya que no tenía Wii. . También me ilusionó mucho que sacaran el Tropical Freeze de WiiU en Switch ya que tampoco tengo WiiU pero sí Switch. Este me avergüenza reconocer que no lo he acabado... 😥 . #nintendo #supernintendo #snes #nintendoswitch #wii #wiiu #nintendo3ds #donkeykong #donkeykongcountry #donkeykongcountry2  #donkeykongcountry3  #donkeykongcountryreturns  #donkeykongcountrytropicalfreeze  #instagamer  #instagamerspain

Game Spyro ™ Reigneted Trilogy merupakan sebuah game yang dikembangkan oleh Toys for Bob dan diterbitkan oleh Activision. Spyro Reigneted Trilogy merupakan koleksi remaster dari 3 game pertama seri Spyro diantaranya Spyro The Dragon  Spyro 2 : Ripto's Rage! dan Spyro : Year of the Dragon.  Game ini mungkin sudah sangat dikenal oleh kalangan gamers  dimana awalnya game ini dirilis pada tahun 1998 untuk Playstation  namun saat ini versi remaster sudah hadir dengan membawa banyak pembaruan dengan masih menampilkan hiasan retro apik era Playstation 1. Game ini sudah dirilis pada tanggal 13 November 2018 untuk platform Playstation 4 dan Xbox One  sedangkan untuk Nintendo Switch dan PC (Steam) dirilis pada tanggal 3 September 2019 kemarin.  Selengkapnya 👇👇 https://www.plutonema.com/2019/09/spyro-reigneted-trilogy-review.html?m=1  #game #spyrothedragon #spyroreignetedtrilogy #playstation4 #xboxone #nintendoswitch #steam #kabargame #indonesiagamers

С выхода новой Зельды - The Legend of Zelda: Link’s Awakening - прошло уже чуть больше недели. За это время я наиграл в неё столько  сколько мне позволяла работа (т.е. очень немного)  но достаточно  чтобы поделиться своим мнением об игре и рассказать вообще  что она из себя представляет! ⠀ Главное  что нужно понять и уяснить - эта и предыдущая (Breath of the Wild) АБСОЛЮТНО разные игры. Не нужно ждать от этой продолжение предыдущей  чтобы не разочароваться🔴 ⠀ Зачем вышла эта игра? Дело в том  что Nintendo решила обновить классику со своей первой портативной консоли  серьезно подтянув ей внешний вид  но практически ничего не меняя по части геймплея. ⠀ В далеком 1993 году The Legend of Zelda: Link’s Awakening стала не только первой игрой серии для дебютной портативной консоли Nintendo  но и была новатором в парочке других областей. Проект  в частности  предложил схему управления  где предметы из инвентаря можно «цеплять» сразу на две клавиши  а заодно подарил Линку возможность прыгать  чего в «Зельде» с видом сверху еще не встречалось. Спустя пять лет  уже на Game Boy Color  вышла обновленная версия  где добавилось небольшое  но красочное подземелье  а монохром сменился цветной картинкой. Сейчас же Link’s Awakening добралась до Switch с кардинально переработанной графикой  однако практически во всем остальном она осталась верна первоисточнику из начала девяностых. ⠀ Игра для меня оказалась очень сложной  за чуть больше недели я собрал 2/8 нужных предметов  игра постоянно вызывает у меня чувство агрессии😆 Но при этом я с огромным удовольствием блуждаю по острову в поисках ответов! Я принципиально не смотрю видеопрохождение (хоть и понимаю  что сдамся в будущем  если буду так тупить) - хочу сам решить все загадки! ⠀ Link’s Awakening больше похожа на музейный экспонат. Его достали из кладовки  сдули пыль  немного отреставрировали и вновь представили публике. На него интересно посмотреть  чтобы понять  как игры работали раньше. Знакомым с оригиналом наверняка захочется узнать  как он преобразился в новой версии. Возможно  для кого-то это будет первая The Legend of Zelda. ⠀ #nintendoswitch #thelegendofzelda

I finally beat the game!!!!! (Golden Deer  Maddening)  It was extremely tough but I really enjoyed the story and gameplay. Lysethia was indeed my best unit throughout the whole game.  With her staff Thyrsus and couple of buff abilities  she became the most reliable glass cannon in my team.  Not to mention that she cleared nearly half of the units in the final mission.  Here is my regular roster for this level Hilda - Great Knight Berna - Bow Knight Dorothea - Gremory Ingrid - Falcon Knight Lysethia - Dark Knight Marianne - Holy Knight Mercedes - Bishop Petra - Assasin Annette - Gremory Claude - Barbossa Byleth - Enlightened One  Yes it was an all-star harem team paradise lol  I think attack range and mobility are most important in this game. I really spammed Lysethia's 'sniping' which helped me clear missions in a breeze. I even gave her all the magic boosting items so that she can become a hyper-carry mage.  I love this game and cannot wait to play a more harder level of this one. Hope there are some more side stories in the DLC!  #fireemblem #fireemblemthreehouses #nintendoswitch #nintendo #lysethia

One of Nintendo’s most successful franchises  “Mario Kart Tour”  is now available for everyone to play on their smartphones. . While it will be a similar gameplay to the Switch  some of its controls and features will be optimised for mobile devices. For example. The multiplayer option will not be available for the meantime but it is expected to be added later on as an in-app purchase option. . A test version of the game developed with partner DeNA Co Ltd featured in-game payment mechanics including gacha where players pay to receive random rewards — such as rare drivers and karts. “It’s going to be a challenge to apply Japanese-style gacha mechanics in the West ” said Michael Pachter  analyst at Wedbush Securities  who sees Mario Kart Tour struggling to hold players’ interest long enough to sustain in-game spending. It also remains to be seen whether Nintendo will be able to square the use of gacha with its famous family-friendly image. . But for the meantime  the app is now available to download on the App Store and the Google Play Store and is totally free to play! Imaginemos que Switch Lite es un vino  Vamos a catarla. Su color destaca  un amarillo mostaza que ensalza los juegos coloridos en pantalla. En las manos  muy cómoda  con un agarre muy confortable y un tacto similar a las fundas de silicona. Su peso  es lo que más llama la atención  pues es muy liviana y sorprende al cogerla por primera vez. En pantalla  apenas apreciamos que es más pequeña  aunque si se nota con las letras. También he apreciado algo más de brillo y saturación de colores que la Switch original. Recomiendo servir con juegos como Mario Kart 8  Mario Maker 2  Links Awakening  Super Smash Bros Ultímate y por supuesto  juegos de SNES Y NES. En mi caso  ha maridado perfectamente con estos. Para el postre  dejo los juegos de ACA Neo Geo  pues un KOF 98 puede ser la guinda. En fin  voy al lío... #nintendoswitch #switchlite #switchliteyellow #nintendo #nin10do #retrogamer #brummelgames #gamer #videojuegos #nintendoswitchlite

Ever pick up a used copy of  Black  white  black 2 and white 2 and ever look at them like "Man i wish i could get the old event mons/items"  Well...what if i told you that In 2019 (2020) you can access them.  With 1 simple non game breaking/ bricking system exploit.  Called: the Dns server trick. This can be preformed with a 3ds family system and can also work for the original ds family line (not dsi line) ------ Without further adu gen 5. How to preform the trick: Step one: Go into your Wi-Fi settings  Step 2. Change the dns settings on your primary Wi-Fi connection Only the primary settings and insert these numbers 164.132.44.106.  Then hit okay and you're done! ---- You can preform this trick with gen 4 but it requires alot more effort that is difficult for me to explain so i have provided a link in my bio for how to do gen 4. ---- What mystery gifts can you get for gen 5?  Well....the mythicals for that gen. For black and white the liberty ticket to get victini Bw2 to get genesect Every single gen 5 Wi-Fi event is available  Even the Japanese  or other country events Note: the events are randomized and some will duplicate so its a gamble to get them all If you have missed any events  or wanted to relive nostalgia then this is the trick for you! These events can be transfered up to gen 7 through pokebank.  Also note for gen 4: if you get the Arceus  Shaymin and darkrai event they can be soft reset to get shiny  This also works for pokemon ranger shadow of almia and guardian signs to get the manaphy egg event mission ------ #pokemon #Bringbacknationaldex #grookey #sobble #scorbunny  #bea #allister #nessa #milo #drednaw #corviknight #wooloo #pokemonsword #pokemonshield  #pokemonswordshield #gamefreak #nintendoswitch #videogame #videogames #grookeygang #sobblesquad #scorbunnysquad #gamefreak  #nintendo #squirtle #curry #squirtlesquad #alcremie #nintendoswitch

Review Summary- Control ===================== SCORE: 9.1 ===================== You looking for a paranormal  sci-fi action game? This is the game for you! I can guarantee you haven't played anything quite like this before.  It has such a unique style and atmosphere  it oozes mystique  and has a certain stillness that keeps you on edge. It's reminiscent of the old Stanley Kubrick classics  so it wouldn't surprise me if that's where they got their inspiration from.  The combat is some of the most fun you'll have this year. Both the gunplay and psychic abilities are polished and each battle is a thrill. You'll always leave the battlefield in a state of choas  thanks to the destructible environments.  The story is full of mystery and will keep you invested  even if it can be a bit confusing at times  especially with the in-game terminology. Extra lore is told through an excessive amount of collectibles  so while there is a lot to learn about this fascinating world  you're constantly stopping to read yet again. It disrupts gameplay and I do wish it was handled more efficiently.  The side missions are just as much of a standout as the main story  with each one containing an interesting and unique storyline  and I always looked forward to each one.  Exploration was one of the weaker elements of the game  as it did get a little frustrating at times getting to where you needed to go. But this was made up by the amount of hidden secrets (and even some good puzzles) scattered around each area.  While it's a relatively short game  I still recommend this to anyone  as it's one of the better games this year. Plus I managed to score the platinum trophy for it  so that's always a bonus! . #control #remedyentertainment #505games #ps4 #playstation4 #playstation #xboxone #xbox #nintendo #nintendoswitch #switch #gamers #gamer #gaming #gaminglife #gamingcommunity #videogames #review #reviews #gamereview #gamingreview #blog #gamingblog #gameswhisperer  Check out my gaming partners and their awesome content:  @lanpartyentertainment  @gameandscotch @7daysaweekblog @royalsunset54 @hitbtojump @gamer_spark_blogger_  @nintygamer @atfirstplay_gaming  @ca_gaming1415

Switch Lite  Japonya’da şu ana kadar ilk haftada en çok satış yapan ikinci oyun konsolu oldu. Nintendo’nun borsadaki hisseleri ise geçtiğimiz günlerde yüzde 4’ten fazla düşüş yaşadı  çünkü yatırımcılar Switch Lite konsolunun iyi satış yapmadığını düşünüyordu. Ancak  Famitsu Magazine’nin verilerine göre durum hiç öyle görünmüyor. Verilere göre Nintendo Switch Lite oyun konsolu  adeta yok sattı ve Japonya’da başlangıç satış rakamı olarak en çok satılan konsollardan birisi oldu. —————————————— #nintendo #nintendoswitch #switch #switchlite #oyun #oyunhaberleri #oyunhaber #oyunkonsolları

Werbung/ Vor 26 Jahren erschien The Legend of Zelda: Link´s Awakening zum ersten Mal – damals für den Game Boy. Jetzt kam das Spiel in neuem Gewand für die Nintendo Switch. Auch diesmal geriet Link auf einer Seereise in ein Unwetter  erleidet Schiffbruch und wird am Strand der Insel Cocolint angespült. Um nach Hause zurückzukehren  muss er herausfordernde Dungeons meistern und furchteinflössende Monster besiegen.  Ein legendäres Spiel im neuen Gewand – The Legend of Zelda: Link`s Awakening macht auf der Nintendo Switch Lite allerhand her. Spielspaß  Begeisterung und Freude im Herzen garantiert. Eine tolle Möglichkeit sich zurück in die Vergangenheit versetzten zu lassen und dem stressigen Alltag ein paar Minuten den Rücken zu kehren.  Mehr dazu gibt es heute auf dem Blog  inkl Gewinnspiel!  #Werbung #Zelda #NintendoDE #Nintendo #nintendoswitch #linksawakening #link #gaming #videogames #NintendoDE #Nintendoswitchlite #produkttester #testen #mamablog #gewinnspiel #dankbar #katerundkissen

Buenas tardes del sabado! Me he pillado una Nintendo switch lite con el Zelda Link’s Awakening! Os voy a dar mi opinión sobre la versión lite respecto a la original. La idea de Nintendo switch es exquisita pero no esta bien llevada a cabo  las guías que tienen para los mandos acaba dando de si y no encajando bien del todo y fallando  el material de los joycon es una castaña y los sensores de movimiento a la mínima que lo tapas un poco lo pierdes aun así es buena consola  sus juegos son la bomba! He de decir que la Nintendo switch lite es perfecta! El tacto nada mas cojerla es increíble respecto a la original  la cruzeta al perder la opción de ser separado es un gustazo   para mi que los fighting me encantan lo agradezco y el peso es perfecto para jugar relajado! Por último la calidad de los botones es mejor! Con todo intento ser crítico y para mi esta es la mejor opción! Dejadme vuestra opinión! Buen fin de semana🍺🍺🎮🎮 . . . . . . . . Marikart tour har äntligen kommit!  Mariokart tour är Nintendos nyaste mobilapp. Där du kör över hela världen med en ny stad varannan vecka. Den första staden vi får köra i är New York som varar de två första veckorna från lanseringen onsdagen den 25:e september. Vi vet att vi kommer få köra i Paris och Tokyo. Som jag har förstått det så kommer staden försvinna efter två veckor. Med varje stad kommer special karaktärer  bilar och fallskärmar. New Yorks är Pauline  musiker Mario  en taxi och ett plan som liknar en taxi tror jag.  Du kan styra med en hand och du väljer om du vill köra med drift eller bara svänga. Alla bilar har en power-up som ger någon sorts fördel i banorna. Sen är vissa gubbar/bilar/fallskärmar bättre på olika banor.  Nintendo har lagt till massa gamla banor från gamla mariokart spel.  OBS! Du behöver ha ett Nintendo konto för att kunna spela. Men dina vänner på switch som har appen kan du skicka vänförfrågan till med typ två tryck. Annars så är det vänkod som på typ alla Nintendos spel.  Om det är någon info ni saknar eller något ni vill veta om spelet så får ni gärna skriva antingen i kommentarerna eller i DM  det är bara kul.  Gå gärna med i min discord server för att kunna prata med mig och lite annat smått och gott. #matheusgaming #mariokart #mariokarttour #nintendo #nintendoapp #nintendoswitch

Mario Kart Tour  Type : Race Size : 596 mb Developer : Nintendo Co. Ltd  Seri permainan balap yang menjadi unggulan di konsol Nintendo Switch hadir resmi di Smartphone kalian! De 1859 com as cartas "Hanafuda"  seguindo até 1981 com o jogo Donkey Kong  onde foi a primeira aparição de Mario com o nome de Jumpman  até os dias atuais com Super mario Odyssey e o mais recente Mario Kat tour  a Nintendo completou 130 anos esse mês. Muitos dizem que a empresa é fraca diante da Sony com seu Playstation e da Microsoft com seu Xbox one  mas a verdade é que ela ano após ano vem trazendo novidades na maneira de se jogar vídeo game  sempre inovando no quesito experiência do jogador. Quem não se lembra do primeiro portátil  do seu primeiro sensor de movimento  do 3D sem óculos e do recente console híbrido!! São 130 anos de cenários belos  grandes aventuras  músicas que ficam na cabeça não importa quando tempo passe e de mínimos detalhes que superam muitas vezes qualquer poder gráfico e permite a cada jogador viver o mesmo jogo de maneiras diferentes. Fica aqui minha homenagem a essa grande empresa que fez e faz parte da vida de muita gente! Parabéns Nintendo 🎁🎊🎉 . . APPLE ARCADE: TUDO O QUE VOCÊ PRECISA SABER  Preço  compatibilidade e informações do serviço de assinatura de games Em março de 2019  a Apple anunciou sua mais nova empreitada no mundo dos games: o Apple Arcade. Disponível tanto para as plataformas mobile quanto computadores e Apple TV  o serviço promete trazer um catálogo de jogos especiais para o público assinante.  Confira abaixo o que é preciso saber sobre o Apple Arcade:  O que é o Apple Arcade? O Apple Arcade é um serviço de assinatura de games  oferecendo acesso ilimitado a mais de 100 títulos para os dispositivos da Apple  tanto mobile quanto no computador e Apple TV.  Lançamento? O serviço foi lançado oficialmente para iPhone em 19 de setembro  junto com o iOS 13. A previsão é de que ele chegue em 30 de setembro para iPad e Apple TV  e outubro para MacBook e iMac  junto do sistema operacional macOS Catalina.  Preço? O Apple Arcade traz um serviço de assinatura de R$ 9 90 por mês  com direito a um mês de teste gratuito.  Jogos? No lançamento  o Apple Arcade conta com um catálogo de mais de 100 jogos. Entre os títulos de destaque estão Oceanhorn 2  Sayonara Wild Hearts  Hot Lava  Where Cards Fall  Frogger in Toy Town e Shinsekai Into the Depths.  Dispositivos compatíveis? Para rodar o Apple Arcade  é necessário ter o iOS 13 no iPhone  iPadOS 13 para iPad  tvOS 13 para Apple TV e macOS Catalina para computadores Mac. Por isso  abaixo estão todos os dispositivos compatíveis com o Apple Arcade: iPhone 6S iPhone 6S Plus iPhone SE iPhone 7 iPhone 7 Plus iPhone 8 iPhone 8 Plus iPhone X iPhone XS iPhone XS Max iPhone XR iPhone 11 iPhone 11 Pro iPhone Pro Max iPad Air 2 iPad Air (3ª. geração) iPad (5ª. geração) iPad Mini 4 iPad Mini (5ª. geração) iPad Pro Apple TV iMac (fim de 2012 ou mais novo) iMac Pro Mac Pro (fim de 2013 ou mais novo) Mac Mini (fim de 2012 ou mais novo) MacBook (fim de 2015 ou mais novo) MacBook Air (meio de 2012 ou mais novo) MacBook Pro (meio de 2012 ou mais novo)  #iphone #apple #games #jogos #videogame #playstation #xbox #nintendo #sega #capcom #konami #nintendoswitch #ps4 #xboxone #atari #microsoft #anime #cinema #filmes #geek #nerd #PC #stadia #sega #paineldogamer

130-летие Nintendo  как это было  Главный игрок в разработке видеоигр отмечает свой 130-й день рождения. Компания начала свою деятельность еще в далеком 1889 году  именно тогда  23 сентября Фусадзиро Ямаути основал Nintendo. Изначально компания занималась продажей игральных карт ханафуда  вплоть до передачи компании внуку Фусадзиро  Хироси. Последний понял  нужно не ограничиваться продажей карт и искать другие варианты расширения компании. Так  компания семейства Ямаути начала заниматься производством игрушек  продажей риса быстрого приготовления  борделями и такси. Из всего выше перечисленного  первое стало самым успешным. В 1966 году была создана игрушка The Ultra Hand  которая стала очень популярной в Японии  это помогло определить дальнейшую судьбу компании. Было создано подразделение Nintendo Games  которое уже в 1970 году представило свой первый продукт  им стал световой пистолет для приставки Magnavox Odyssey. В 1977 году Nintendo объединяется с Mitsubishi  плодом их совместной работы стала приставка Color TV-Game 6  с вшитой аркадной игрой понг. Звездный путь компании начался с игровой системы на картриджах Famicom (NES)  которая поступила в продажу в 1983 году. Благодаря этой приставке  Nintendo обрела популярность за пределами родины  покорив рынок видеоигр в Европе и США. Если коротко в цифрах  за 130 лет Nintendo выпустила 10 консолей  среди которых самыми популярными стали Nintendo DS  Game Boy  Wii и ныне популярная Switch. Общее количество проданных копий «четверки»  составило около 411 миллионов. At first  the split up between internet superstar Tyler "Ninja" Blevins and Twitch seemed to be going relatively smoothly. However  the tone between the two seems to have soured as of late  especially after an incident in which porn was accidentally shown on Ninja's former Twitch channel. Now  Ninja has called Twitch out over another recent event on the game streaming website. . Blevins posted a brief video on Twitter following the Twitch Con opening ceremony  during which the company addressed transparency regarding with bans on the service  largely due to recent incidents on the platform with seemingly arbitrary punishments. In the video  Blevins seems to criticize Twitch over the mishandling of the incident in which streamer Alinity threw her cat over her head during a stream  stating  "All right  so here's what you did wrong. . بازی FIFA 20 نسخه Legacy Edition برای نینتندو سوییچ . با بازی فیفا 20، فوتبال، این ورزش همگانی و محبوب، بار دیگر به کنسول‌های خانگی شما می‌آید و با فیزیک متفاوت توپ، بهتر از همیشه به نظر می‌رسد. بازی فیفا 20 دارای صدها تیم از سراسر دنیا و مسابقات بزرگی مانند لیگ قهرمانان اروپا است تا هیجان فوتبال را در دستان خود حس کنید و با مود FIFA Ultimate Team، بازیکنان مورد نظر خود را در یک تیم جمع کنید و با دیگر بازیکنان در سراسر دنیا رقابت کنید. .  بخش فوتبال خیابانی که ولتا خطاب می‌شود، تجربه‌ای جدید و کاملا متفاوت از فوتبال است و در زمین‌های مختلف در سرتاسر دنیا، با بهترین بازیکنان فوتبال بازی می‌کنید. تکنیک و مهارت در فوتبال خیابانی حرف اول را می‌زنند. . بازی FIFA 20 Legacy Edition دارای منوها، رابط کاربری و مدل جدید گزارش بازی‌ها به همراه آخرین آپدیت تیم‌ها و استادیوم‌ها است، اما از نظر گیم پلی هیچ گزینه جدیدی نسبت به فیفا 19 وجود ندارد. . این بازی دارای مودهای بازی دوستانه، کریر، تورنمنت‌های لایسنس شده، فصل آنلاین، بازی دوستانه آنلاین و فصل‌های آفلاین در کنار FIFA Ultimate Team خواهد بود و گیم پلی به کار گرفته شده، همان گیم پلی بازی فیفا 19 است. . 💸 جهت اطلاع از قیمت محصول به وبسایت ما مراجعه کنید یا در قسمت نظرات همان محصول بیان نمایید. . برچسب ها:  #بازی #گیم #گیمینگ #محصولات_گیمینگ #نینتندو #نینتندوسوییچ #نینتندوسوییچ_لایت #نینتندو_سوئیچ #نینتندو_سوییچ #نینتندو_ایران #پرو_گیمر #فیفا #فیفا۲۰ #فیفا20 #فیفا2020 #game #gaming #games #Nintendo #nintendoswitchlite #nintendoswitch #fifa #fifastreet #fifa20 #fifa2020 #سرخ_کالا

➡️➡️ Swipe to see gameplay➡️➡️ . . Playing some Kirby Star Stacker on SNES. I really like how they still went with the crayon style graphics like Yoshi’s Island. Game looks like an obvious tie in to Kirby Dream Land 3 which was released months later. Though I’m disappointed with how short the game is. I feel like it was rushed and not too much heart was put into this. I kind of expected a little more from this one even though we do get a new character Gryll after this title the character never made any appearances afterwards in the Kirby series and recently is a spirit in Smash Bros Ultimate. This version of Star Stacker is rare and is the only Japan exclusive Kirby title we never got in the west. Being released exclusively on SF Memory Cassette carts on the Super Famicom  it eventually did get a retail release but there’s a small about of copies and is expensive especially in CIB. If you’ve played Star Stacker on your GameBoy I don’t think your missing out much on this title unless you don’t have access to a link cable or another copy. But still the original GameBoy port of Star Stacker is much more cheaper and you get to see it pop out nicely on your Super GameBoy.  #kirby #kirbystarstacker #kirbykirakirakids #snes #16bit #kirbysdreamland3 #puzzlegames #superfamicom #kirbysdreamland #supernintendo #nintendo #nintendoswitch #retrogaming #importgaming #japanesevideogames #kirbyssuperstarstacker #kirbyssparklingkids #カービィのきらきらきっず  #カービィ #任天堂 #supersmashbros #スーパーファミコン #ニンテンドー #gameboy #星のカービィ#gamer #gaming #retrocollective

On-going review- Control ==================== My last post before I wrap up my review tomorrow. Now I've been mostly positive about this game so far  but it's not perfect  and there were a couple of things that held it back from true greatness.  I already talked about the excessive amounts of collectibles in my last post. It's fine to have a lot of extra lore  but surely there was a more efficient way to go about it.  My other main issue was how useless the map was. Maybe use it as a rough guide  but not to go exactly where you need to go. A lot of areas are multi-story  and the map just shows everything in one clump. If you're trying to get from one room to another  the map be more misleading than anything  and I did get frustrated quite a few times trying to get around.  When you think of maps from other games  like Resident Evil 2  they're laid out so clearly it helps makes exploration more fun because you're not wasting time looking at blank walls where the map says there should a doorway.  But I will admit my criticisms are fairly minor and didn't detract too much from the fun overall. Happy National @dragonquest Day  everybody!  I hope everyone’s enjoying the release of Dragon Quest XI and I  II  and III on the Switch. Thought I’d whip up a couple slimes for Procreate practice to celebrate.  Even though they’re palette swaps in the game  I like all the varieties to have their own distinct shape and body language. Originals are smaller  oval shaped  and squishier. She-slimes are rounder and a little more solid. Metal slimes are more a circle with a spikier top. Mottle slimes are the tallest and are shaped more like a ball. It’s fun to come up with all the different ways to put personality in them.  #dragonquest #dragonquestxi #squareenix #nintendoswitch #slime #ドラゴンクエスト #ドラゴンクエスト11 #ドラクエ #procreate #characterdesign

Children Of Morta es un juego desarrollado por Dead Mage que ya está disponible en early access y espera a su lanzamiento en consolas a partir del 15 de octubre. Esta entrega es un juego de RPG de acción que cuenta la historia de una familia de héroes a la cual controlaremos a través de un mundo generado de manera procedural. Tanto su estética pixel art como su jugabilidad son sus alegatos principales. Primero Contamos con un juego que trae unas animaciones extraordinarias y luego un sistema de progresión muy bien trabajado el cual se extiende hasta seis personajes que en conjunto con el combate que es divertido y equilibrado hacen de éste un juego muy entretenido.  #childrenofmorta #deadmage #indie #game #gamer #gaming #videogame #videojuego #ps4 #playstation #nintendo #nintendoswitch #switch #xboxone #xbox #microsoft #pc #pcgaming #pcgamer #pcgame #roguelike #mazmorras #mazmorra

True Rare Rating - 9.2  Limited Edition GameStop Managers Yoshi's Island DS Sweepstakes Statue. Production numbers unknown but very likely under 50 made.  In November 2006 Yoshi's Island DS was released. To reward the GameStop managers who had the most pre-orders there was a questionnaire sent out to each store that reached a specific number of pre-order sales. if the questionnaire was filled out and sent back to corporate that particular manager was put into a sweepstakes drawing for this awesome Yoshi's Island Statue.  The winners did not get them until late the following year and many of the managers who won were no longer employed for the company 😂 Those that did get them and were still around found that their shipment was commonly broken.  There have only been a dozen or so seen circulating  and many of them were broken during reshipment. This is very much a dwindling supply asset due to fragility.  Sealed copy of Yoshi's Island included for scale.  #Nintendo #nintendoswitch #nintendolife #nintendo64 #nintendo3DS #nintendofan #nintendoworld #nintendods #nintendopower #nintendogames #NintendoWiiU #nintendowii #nintendoart #nintendoentertainmentsystem #nintendogamecube #Nintendomemes #nintendocollection #Nintendo3DSxl #nintendogamer #nintendocosplay #nintendogram #nintendouk #nintendovibes #nintendocollector #nintendotattoo #nintendofamily #nintendomeme #nintendo2ds #yoshi #yoshisisland

I just finished Link’s Awakening for the Switch  and I’m still smiling! 😃 What a brilliant  and masterful remake of a 26 year old classic.  I never played the original back in 93 on the Gameboy  but I know it’s always been considered one of the best Zelda games to date.  So I was going in fresh  and boy did I have a blast!  This game is a prime example of how consistent Nintendo is  and how well their games age.  Except for the obvious visual overhaul (which is out of this world cute) and a few quality of life improvements  it’s identical to it’s older brother…and it holds up incredibly well.  It’s a reminder of just how meticulously crafted this game is.  If you’re a fan of Zelda games  especially the older ones…you owe it to yourself to check this one out. | #nintendoswitch #nintendo #zelda #linksawakening

So I must say  upon initial reaction to the ending of Tag  my reaction in my previous post still holds truth. However. - - After lots of reading  listening to radios  and watching YouTube videos  I can not say Tag is a bad map. Its truthfully brilliant once you give it some thought  and delivers a tragic ending no one saw coming. - - I will however  say that Tag is still a disappointing map to what they were building up. All we heard about since origins was “The Great War”. All through Blops4  it seemed to be the main point of focus leading up to Tag  giving most of us the impression we would be participating. Like I had hoped. - - Instead  we were completely thrown for a loop. Given something we just did not expect. So now this beckons the question  was this a bad thing? I dont think so. I actually think on Treyarch’s end  if their resources were as limited as its been rumored  was pretty brilliant. Because they pulled it off. - - Its a beautiful map. A nice reimagination of Call of the Dead  which really was one of my favorite maps ever. The radios are super interesting  the wonder weapons are pretty decent and easy to get  and it really plays like old school zombies. - - The ending makes sense too. Given all things considered and understanding their ultimate sacrifice  it is actually really beautiful. Its sad. It actually does make you think once you’re given more context. Once you understand  there was no way to end the cycle with all them existing. It didnt matter how they changed the future  their existence as a whole was the fracture that threw the very universe into chaos. - - Now i ask you  what do you think? I want to know your opinions  feel free to drop a comment or DM me personally. - - #blackops4 #blackops #zombies #tagdertoten #treyarch #playstation4 #ps4 #xboxone #callofduty #cod #modernwarfare #review #gaming #videogames #fortnite #pubg #nintendo #nintendoswitch

Super Kirby Clash – Análisis uper Kirby Clash no es ni de lejos un juego por el que nadie se vaya a volver loco  pero desde luego con paciencia puede ser disfrutado por quien se acerque a él. Como es costumbre en la saga esta dirigido a todos los públicos  y resulta un juego fácil  aunque su apartado gráfico es muy agradable y su estilo de juego lo hace ideal para cuando tengamos 5 minutos y queramos disfrutar de una partida rápida a algo. Además los micropagos no nos permiten avanzar demasiado deprisa por mucho que nos guste el juego  a no ser que paguemos  así que quien quiera disfrutarlo sin pagar puede jugar un rato al día para no gastar todas sus gemas de golpe. Ya que de lo contrario hay que esperar demasiado para recolectar las suficientes para poder desbloquear misiones suficientes para volver a disfrutar de una sesión de juego algo más duradera. En definitiva no suspende en ningún apartado pero tampoco destaca excesivamente en ninguno  a excepción tal vez de los combates que podamos realizar con amigos en la misma consola  donde más fuerte y divertido se muestra este Kirby... Level-5 has changed the title of the Inazuma Eleven Ares game to Inazuma Eleven: Great Road of Heroes and announced a spring 2020 release window for Japan. . In a blog post  Level-5 apologized for the miscalculations that have occurred in development thus far  which resulted in the Inazuma Eleven Ares anime series and its sequel Inazuma Eleven: Orion no Kokuin to conclude before the release of the game. However  development of the game has since moved from an outsourced to a fully in-house development system  which has allowed further system revisions to create a game with more exciting battles. . Inazuma Eleven: Great Road of Heroes is based on the drama of Inazuma Eleven Ares and features additional episodes in which past characters also appear. . Like previous Inazuma Eleven titles  the game system will offer a high level of freedom in which player positions are indicated by the controller (or mouse). It promises to be a completely new type of RPG that incorporates eSports developments  as well as enhanced hack-and-slash elements such as battles and player gatherings. Level-5 also hopes to make a deep online system with a wide range of tactics in whch national tournaments can be held. . Inazuma Eleven: Great Road of Heroes is in development for PlayStation 4  Switch  iOS  and Android. . #InazumaElevenGreatRoadOfHeroes #level5 #InazumaElevenAres #football #soccer #anime #animation #manga #playstation4 #playstation #ps4 #switch #nintendo #nintendoswitch #ios #android #smartphone #vg4n_InazumaElevenGreatRoadOfHeroes . Chegou ontem  novinho  lacrado e arrasani. Agora que testei posso falar algumas impressões. Acho que pelo preço que é comercializado no Brasil não vale a pena ser comprado de jeito nenhum. É melhor comprar outro jogo ou juntar mais um pouco e comprar o wireless. Um sonho para quem é altx e tem a mão grande e um pesadelo para quem é pequenininhx. Ele é mais robusto  cansa menos a mão  mais leve e é lindo. No entanto ele não tem uma das funções principais que é o sensor de movimento e o rumble  então  a depender do que você vai jogar fica impossível ou quase isso. Em todo caso se você se apaixonou e continua muito querendo um mesmo assim tenta no Mercado Livre  lá é muito mais em conta do que comprar em loja de shopping. #nintendoswitchgames #nintendoswitch #breathofthewild #transboynerd #thelegendofzelda #botw #lgbtgeeks #lgbtnerds #zelda #nintendolife #nintendobrasil

FIFA sempre foi um grande game e nos últimos anos ele dominou o cenário de jogos de esportes nos videogames  porém  já não é de hoje que jogadores vem reclamando das poucas novidades no jogo em seu modo off-line e das práticas abusivas em seu modo online que sempre dividiu opiniões entre os fãs. Com o lançamento do FIFA2020  as opiniões ainda continuam divididas  já que o "Modo Volta" futebol de rua (famoso Fifa Street) não era lá o que os fãs queriam  afinal de contas seu concorrente Pro evolution Soccer vem trazendo muitas novidades em ralação aos anos anteriores  O destaque principal vai para jogabilidade que está cada vez mais real  algo que os fãs de FIFA viram o game  perder com o passar dos anos. Mas a pergunta que não quer calar é: FIFA vai se encontrar e manterá o seu reinado ou Pro Evolution Soccer irá depois de anos voltar a ser o queridinho dos jogadores? Happy Dragon Quest XI S Day.🐉🎉🎊🎉 A new amazing addition to the series  or well.. a port remake with an addition of 2D mode + extra stuffs..😍 Its my first time going through both viii and xi . But currently only just started DQ VIII.😁. Just finished vii yesterday and its the most longest for a DQ game ever lol.😂. With DQ XI S (been waiting for this version from the start) out  its finally time to embark on the journey of another hero in another world/Realm. Tbh all DQ games are all kinda have that same thing plot wise  idk bout i ii  and iii cuz never had the chance to try them. But for iv-vii  and ix. its kinda same thing all over again. Just different kind of approach for characters story but all the same for endgame.😄 Each characters are unique in their own ways.😂 Love to see some variations.😍🤣 Now im ready to experience DQ Viii and DQ Xi. DQ XI S is an evolved form of DQ VIII from its battle mechanics and well u start using skill points to assign skills and abilities instead of doing vocations (freedom to built your jobs) for each characters. DQViii was the start of all that where each characters learn their own specific spells/abilities depending on their own unique weapon skill sets that comes together with how each character can handle specific kinds of weapons.⚔🏹🛡 Definitely gonna have fun with both titles.👍More amazing titles coming up in the next few months  definitely gonna check them out. Hope everyone have a wonderful days ahead and remember to have fun at your own time and pace.👋😄 . . #nintendo  #dragonquestxi #dragonquestxiechoesofanelusiveage  #dragonquestxisechoesofanelusiveagedefinitiveedition  #gamer  #instagaming  #squareenix #jrpg #nintendo3ds #switch #nintendoswitch  #dragonquestviii #dragonquestvii #gaming #dqxi #dqxis

Sejak bulan Maret 2019  penjualan game New Super Mario Bros U. Deluxe telah mencapai angka 4 1 juta! 😲  New Super Mario Bros U. Deluxe bergenre platform game seperti halnya game Super Mario Bros yang kalian kenal selama ini 😉. Layaknya ciri khas game Super Mario Bros  kalian akan berpetualang sebagai Mario atau Luigi untuk menyelamatkan Peach dari Bowser (again) 😅. Kali ini kalian tidak hanya berpetualang sendirian untuk menyelamatkan Peach karena game ini dapat dimainkan hingga 4 orang sekaligus dalam game ini 😃. Kalian juga dapat memilih nih ingin berperan sebagai Mario  Luigi  Toad  Toadette  atau Nabbit di mana mereka memiliki kelebihan dan kekurangan masing-masing 👌. Oleh karena itu  semakin banyak pemainnya maka kalian semakin akan melengkapi. 🙈  Nah jika kalian ingin tahu keseruan New Super Mario Bros U. So I’ve seen a lot of people upset about Luigi not being in Mario Kart Tour and rightfully so. However these gacha games are always adding characters and putting them as spotlights for the weekly banner. And what better way to kick off October with its first new banner being LUIGI who has a game coming out later that month! Also these mobile games like to throw holiday events especially for Halloween (Think of Dragalia Lost for example) and a Luigi’s Mansion themed banner would be PERFECT for a Halloween event. Plus this is a perfect advertising opportunity for Luigi’s Mansion 3! To show you what this would look like I made 2 mock-up screens of the banner and description like they did for Pauline. I think they would add Luigi (obviously) his Poltergust 4000 Kart from Mario Kart DS a Luigi’s Mansion themed glider and either bring back the Luigi’s Mansion course from the DS or make a brand new course based on the hotel from the new game. Sometimes I think about editing myself perfect - making my eye bags vanish  tucking away the hair poking out from my wigs. That's what I love about editing my own photos. I get to decide what I want people to see  and what I want to conceal. Lately  I've  been thinking a lot about the way attractiveness plays into your worth  whether that be measured by yourself or others. Everything online is fake  including this photo. Remember that. In the end  are you seeing people's hopes and dreams through a lense of their own creation  or a desperation to be a person they are not? There's my late night deep thought for y'all.  #link #snowquilllink #snowquillarmor #legendofzelda #nintendo #breathofthewild #botw #lozcosplay #cosplay #bigbeautifulcosplay #plussizecosplay #nintendoswitch #womenofcosplay #gamergirl

So… I just finished playing my first fire emblem three houses playthrough with the golden deer. The only other fire emblem game I played was fates: birthright but I never finished it and it did not grab my attention like three houses did. What I can say is that I loved this game  despite there being thing that I did not like/hated in it  but I  still loved the game through and through. I know that there are other routes  but I am planning on playing the GD route again and plan to recruit everyone into my house  so I will most likely watch a playthough on the other routes or play the other routes myself later in time. I can honestly say that this is one of the biggest if not the biggest Nintendo switch game of this year and I would highly recommend playing this game. I know there are people who do not like strategy rpg games and I understand that because I do not really like the genre like that  but give this game a chance at least. Alright I’m done talking and I will talk to you all later. . . . . . . . . . . . . •Cuando pasé Link’s Awakening para la Game Boy justo pasaba por un momento triste en mi vida  la pérdida de un ser querido. Y pues la historia de este juego me enseñó  de forma subjetiva  a lidiar con una pérdida  el irnos de un lugar en el que sabemos que no vamos a regresar jamás  el aprender a soltar y vivir con lo que esa persona o ese lugar nos ha enseñado. Por eso es un juego muy especial para mi. Y yo se qué la interpretación de este juego es muy subjetiva  y que quizá estoy volando mucho pero me gustaría analizar los videojuegos desde este ángulo también  un poco con teorías y formas distintas de verlos. ¿Qué dicen  les gustaría videos así? 🤔 . . . #linksawakening #nintendoswitch #nintendo #zelda #thelegendofzelda #link #videogames #videogame #youtube #youtube #games #videojuegos #gameboy

#fireemblem #fireemblemthreehouses #goldendeer #nintendo #nintendoswitch #videogames #videogamecollection  Ok  so I got this a few weeks back on day of release but only started playing it about four weeks ago  and man this fucking game had it's hooks in me from the start! I'm a big fan of this franchise so I had really been anticipating this one when it was announced about two years ago and it did not let down...well the ending could have been a bit better but that wasn't enough to ruin the experience I had. I can't recall the last time I put this much time into a game and it was a blast. Once the future dlc drops I'm probably gonna start a new game. This is a strategy RPG with life sim mechanics so it's not for everyone  but if you've ever been curious about these type of games this is a great game to start. ✌

... y ese motivo es poder usar las dos consolas como si fuera una. Al contrario que Nintendo 3DS  donde teníamos que eliminar y borrar los datos de una  para usar la otra  con la Cuenta Nintendo  no pasa. Podemos usar nuestra cuenta en Switch y Switch Lite  al mismo tiempo  compartiendo online  juegos digitales y el guardado de partidas en la nube. Solo una pega; la consola secundaria  necesita conexión a internet permanente  para poder jugar. Pero  he aquí la jugada; convertir en consola principal nuestra Lite  y como secundaria  la Switch original. Con este “setup” mi Switch original se queda en casa  con conexión permanente  y conectada a la TV  y la Lite la uso exclusivamente como portátil  y así poder jugar  sin necesitar conexión. Con el guardado en la nube  puedo descargar todas mis partidas y seguir jugando. Obviamente  tener los dos sistemas no es necesario. Pero si compartimos esta afición  tener ambas   puede ser una opción interésante  y disfrutar de las bondades de ambos sistemas. Por el momento  estoy llevándome la Switch Lite a todos lados  cuando antes  era más reservado  y me daba “cosa” llevármela según donde. En breves me voy de viaje y podré probarla a fondo. Espero haber arrojado algo de luz a vuestras dudas! #nintendoswitch #nintendoswitchlite #nintendo #brummelgames #gamer #videogames #nin10do #nintendoswitch #retrogamer #gamerroom #switch #nintendo3ds

Seven days of #kookievision  based on my latest Link's Awakening sugar cookie set. Day four. Chain Chomp. Yes  he's a Mario character  but here's a fun fact: did you know that he was originally created as a Zelda enemy? He makes an appearance in a few of the Legend of Zelda games  actually. In Link's Awakening  Madam MeowMeow of Mabe Village has a pet Chain Chomp in her front yard named BowWow. Link's Awakening is full of odes to Mario - not just this guy!  If you want to see more  I created a 20 minute video compilation of the entire set. No instructions  no dialogue  just some music. ”Final Fantasy VII establishes A New Standard Of Excellence For PlayStation Games” And This Headline Still Stands Strong Today In 2019 - This Is A Rare And Original Final Fantasy VII Midgar EU Exclusive “Not For Sale” Promo Postcard ; Promoting It’s November 14th Release In 1997 In Europe With It’s Original Price of £44.99 . One of my personal and original favourites ofc for the Midgar art but also I love the back of the Card itself as it has some very interesting info which talks about FFVII and it’s phenomenal success in Japan and US alongside some mini reviews and scores for the game where PlayStation gave it a 10/10 aswell as it’s original price of £44.99   I specifically love the quote they used about the game having 3 discs and saying “ That will take a lifetime to complete” cause then FFVIII and FFIX then went onto have 4 discs each i just find that so retro and funny how they highlighted that in particular before the days of DVD discs 👌🏻 . This postcard was only obtained through Promotional Purposes Prior to its EU Release and couldn’t be bought  they seem to be very rare nowadays would look great framed . #game #games #gamer #gaming #gamers #videogames #finalfantasy #kingdomhearts #squareenix #ps4 #playstation #ps1 #finalfantasy7 #ffvii #picoftheday #pictureoftheday #nintendo #xbox #cloudstrife #jrpg #retro #anime #japan #nintendoswitch #rpg #art #ff7remake #finalfantasycollection #finalfantasyvii #playstation4

Quando alguém disser que videogame é coisa de desocupado  mostre isso😅  De acordo com um representante da Força Aérea Real Britânica  os gamers estão na mira de grandes empresas e do exército para ocupar cargos relevantes  “a capacidade de assimilar informações  reagir rapidamente em situações extremas  coordenando ações enquanto se mantém o foco sob pressão  são atributos comuns aos jogadores profissionais de videogames”. Na onda dessa novidade  a empresa Game Academy viu nos jogadores a oportunidade de potencializar o uso dessas habilidades no ambiente de trabalho e futuramente podem  até constar nos currículos. "Os empregadores exigem liderança na hora de contratar  então  posso incluir no currículo meus anos liderando ataques no World of Warcraft!"  afirmou David Barrie  um dos fundadores da Game Academy.  O preconceito contra os gamers tem diminuído à medida que as empresas comprovam a eficiência de quem joga videogame em cargos de importância e trabalhos em grupos  Matthew Ricci  que joga EVE Online  basicamente já possuí um mestrado em administração de empresas. Como diretor de uma corporação com centenas de jogadores no game  há quatro anos ajuda marcas internacionais a ingressar no mercado canadense dentro dessa parceria. Ryan Gardner  diretor de recrutamento profissional  enfatizou que as habilidades sociais dos jogadores podem ser utilizadas em um ambiente profissional  como o trabalho em equipe  a resolução de problemas à curto prazo e o planejamento estratégico. Então  quando alguém disser que jogar não dá futuro  já sabe!  Life Is A Game! Via: David Molloy BBC  #progamer #gaming #game #ps4 #xboxone #nintendoswitch #pcgamer

Guitar hero  foi um game de explodir cabeças em época das poucas locadoras de games que ainda restavam  já que se via o game competindo nesse tipo de lugar com outros games gigantes : GTA : San Andreas e Pro evolution Soccer. Quem jogava se sentia um verdadeiro astro do Rock ainda mais quando se jogava com o controle na versão de Guitarra  aí pronto.. Eram horas e horas na frente da TV sem piscar pra não errar nenhuma nota 😵. 💚 My Stardew Valley Farmer 💚 . this took a lotttttt more effort than I was expecting. I also got this idea from @krillustration so all credit goes to them for the inspiration! . can I just say  I think it’s hilarious that one of my best friends is the Wizard 😂 he’s so rude but I love it! Shane also almost made the cut  but not quite. and f*** the green slimes 😑 actually  ALL coloured slimes can go to hell lol they’re so annoying... . ANYWAYS! I really pushed myself with this one and made sure I stepped out of my comfort zone and I’m so glad I stuck it out til the end. two years ago if you told me I would eventually design a character with just a pixel icon to go off of (or just design an entire character at all) I probably wouldn’t have believed you... I know there’s so much more room for improvement but I’m glad that I can personally see my own growth in my pieces 😇 . NINTENDO SWITCH LITE. Консоль для тех  кто любит играть в пути.  Nintendo Switch Lite — новое пополнение в семействе Nintendo Switch. Компактная и легкая консоль со встроенным управлением.  Nintendo Switch Lite поддерживает все игры Nintendo Switch  в которые можно играть в портативном режиме. Консоль отлично подойдет для тех  кто много играет вне дома  и для тех  кто хочет играть в сетевом или локальном мультиплеере с друзьями и родными  у которых уже есть флагманская модель Nintendo Switch.  Консоль Nintendo Switch Lite предназначена для портативного гейминга  поэтому ее нельзя подключить к телевизору. ⚠️В НАЛИЧИИ В МАГАЗИНЕ @digitalhouse_minsk !  #nintendoswitch #nintendoswitchlite

Does anyone else Remember Minecade? Well  if you don't  then I can't say I blame you. Minecade was a server network that was popular in the Java edition of Minecraft for a short while. One of the most popular games on it was Super Craft Bross  which was basically Kit PVP with double jumping and special abilities. Sethbling  a Minecraft YouTuber who specializes in making mechanics and contraptions  was a pretty big face of the server for a while.  However  as time went by  things around the server started to go downhill. Updates for Super Craft Bros. were few and far between. Balancing issues and bugs were rarely if ever  fixed. To make things worse  Minecraft's popularity was in a lull. It was around this time I quit playing on Minecade because the games I liked just weren't fun to play anymore.  Fast forward to now. With Minecraft getting a bit of an extra life when it comes to mainstream popularity  I wondered what Minecade has been up to. Last I checked  they could barely break 50 players  and those players were mostly on a rather basic creative server. When I went to the website  all I found was  well  this. The website is a mess. I’ve also checked around a few forums and can’t find much.  So. What happened to Minecade? I’ll keep looking. #minecraft #videogames #videogame #game #gamer #gaming #playstation #ps4 #xbox #xboxone #pc #nintendo #nintendoswitch *puts on detective hat*

El nivel usa las distintas mecánicas que hay disponible para los Thwomps  y me aseguré que tenga fases llenas de emoción y diversión. Pese a que tiene una dificultad considerable (sobretodo para los más casuales) es posible completarlo luego de practicarlo  les recomiendo dedicarle tiempo. Por cierto  si desean una dificultad aún mayor  es posible conseguir el Final Verdadero! Para conseguirlo  deberán recolectar las 8 monedas escondidas por todo el nivel (esto es totalmente opcional). Algunas requerirán una prueba de habilidad  y otras les obligaran a pensar un poco más (pero hay pistas escondidas en todo el nivel). Si deciden emprender esta aventura extra  les deseo mucha suerte! Y nada más  mándenme sus opiniones  críticas y capturas cuando lo pasen  si llegan al True Ending con más razón! Mucha suerte y diviértanse! I’ve been steadily picking at 'Fire Emblem Three Houses' for the past month or so and while I admit I haven’t quite finished the game I can say confidently that it is one of my favorites of the year. While I don’t have a ton of experience with the Fire Emblem series it's hard to imagine the diehards finding too much at fault with it’s core gameplay. The turn based “rock paper scissors” battles the series is iconic for are so engaging and addictive to play and beautifully presented. There’s something so epic about having the camera rapidly zoom in to the ground level of the battlefield so you can watch your characters duke it out. But I think the crowning achievement of this game is its story and narrative structure. You play as “The Professor” a sort of blank slate character who finds him or herself teaching at a prestigious military academy. In between battles you will fill your time lecturing and getting to know your students (who of course are your soldiers in battles) all the while completing side quests around the school. It’s essentially a lighter but more focused version of what the Persona series does. Within the first couple hours of play I found myself really caring for my students and motivated to prepare them as effectively as I could so they wouldn’t die in combat (yes perma-death is still a thing if you want it). This along with a storyline that evolves and twists based on your actions and choices makes for an immensely satisfying narrative experience. YU-NO: A Girl Who Chants Love at the Bound of this World llegará en formato físico

YU-NO: A Girl Who Chants Love at the Bound of this World es una novela visual con toques de rol que nos meterá en la piel de Takuya Arima una joven estudiante que durante sus vacaciones recibe un misterioso paquete que contiene un dispositivo reflector que permite viajar entre mundos paralelos.

Con la ayuda de sus amigos Takuya debe descubrir el misterio del legado de su padre un investigador que ha llevado a cabo diversos estudios sobre astrofísica y que desapareció en extrañas circunstancias.

1993 GIOCAVO CON IL MIO GB GRIGIO A TETRIS. UN MIO AMICO  NON RICORDO ESATTAMENTE  MI DISSE "IO QUESTO GIOCO NON LO CAPISCO  FACCIAMO CAMBIO CHE IO A TETRIS NON CI HO MAI GIOCATO?" ALLORCHÉ  INGENUAMENTE  GLI DISSI DI NO. QUALCHE GIORNO DOPO  SEMPRE LUI "DAI  ANGELO  FACCIAMO CAMBIO SOLO PER UNA SETTIMANA" STANCO DELLE SUE LAMENTELE (ERO SOCIOPATICO GIÀ DALLA TENERA ETÀ) ACCONSENTII. IL GIOCO ERA "THE LEGEND OF ZELDA - LINK'S AWAKENING". QUESTO OMINO CHE GIRAVA A ZONZO PER QUESTA ISOLA CON UNA SPADA E UNO SCUDO. "MA CHE CACATA È QUESTA" PENSAI. DOPO AVER FINITO I COMPITI  QUEL GIORNO  MI RIMISI A GIOCARE.  DOPO UN'ORETTA BUONA  AVEVO CAPITO LA MECCANICA DI GIOCO ED ENTRATO  PER PURO CASO  NEL PRIMO DUNGEON. Well  this was seriously the better part of three houses. It wasn't as good as blue lions but better than Rhea's route  definitely better. Characters were the same of course but with new game plus it was easier to improve their skills and power as well as the support ranks. The story was better 'cause we were the "bad appearing but actually good" guys instead of the other way around (where we fought for the actual villain basically... 'till we killed them too). The Final fight wasn't really satisfying (and way easier than in Rhea's route...)  this was probably the easiest boss fight in Fire emblem I even had... Except every boss fight in fricking Fates. I was also surprised (with an piece of disappointment) what this route did with Dedue  that was something Dedue would literally never do and I really didn't liked how the blue lions were showed. I'm glad that I saved Felix with recruiting him... And Ashe... And Lysithia from Golden Deers too. Speaking of  next and last route Golden Deers  I'm looking forward to the meme house. This route gets an 7.5/10 © Intelligente Systems  Nintendo  Shouzou Kaga #fireemblem #fireemblemthreehouses #nintendoswitch #nintendo #jrpg #japaneseroleplayinggame #videogames #game #gaming #animecommunity #mangacommunity #anime #japan #otaku #manga

A LucasArts ficou famosa nos anos 90 por seus jogos de Point and Click e um dos títulos mais amados por todos foi o Grim Fandango. O jogo é derivado da comemoração mexicana do Dia de los Muertos  onde nosso protagonista deve descobrir quem está por trás de uma cadeia de corrupção no Mundo dos Mortos e é válido lembrar que esse foi o primeiro título em 3D lançado pela empresa. Em 2015 tivemos uma desmaterialização de Grim Fandango que incluía também legendas e dublagem em português do Brasil. Quem não teve a chance de jogar  fica a dica de um jogo divertido e com uma temática atípica nos videogames. #grimfandango #lucasarts #pointandclick #xbox360 #xboxone #microsoft #playstation #playstation2 #playstation3 #playstation4 #ps1 #psone #ps2 #ps3 #ps4 #sony #nintendo #nintendoswitch #switch #pcgamer #arcades #jogatina #gaming #videogames

BATMAN ARKHAM Y ROCKSTEDY HACIENDO HISTORIA . Quien no conoce la saga de batman arkham   pero pocos conocen su pasado antes de el primer batman arkham  se estaba desarrollando por parte de pandémic studios un juego basado en la película de christopher nolan batman the dark knigth  lastimosamente a pandemic studios nunca se les dio a entender que el juego tenia que estar basado en la película del mismo nombre y con pocos meses que tenían para finalizar el juego y EA presionándolos para finalizarlo por que si no lo hacían perdían la licencia finalmente el proyecto fue cancelado también causando el cierre de pandemic  studios . Después warner brothers games  se decidió de darle la oportunidad a un pequeño estudio que tenia en ese momento poco mas de 35 empleados este studio  era ROCKSTEDY que decidió de darse la tarea de adaptar la historia de los cómics ARKHAM ASYLUM y contrataron a dos de las voces mas conocidas por sus personajes en la serie animada de BATMAN y esos son kevin konroy como BATMAN y mark hammil COMO EL JOKER  después de todo esto rockstedy finalizo el juego y lo lanzo al mercado siendo un gran éxito y después... . . . Te gusta la historia y quieres mas de historias así? I know I sound entitled and spoiled but I miss my game room so much. When I tried getting my things I could only make it out with a few consoles and a few games before the police got there. The games dont even go to the consoles  but I'm thankful for what I did get. Those of you who had played games with me and took one step into my game room knew how passionate I was about taking care of them and the history they had. It breaks my heart to see almost all of it gone. Videogames were such a big part of my life. The memories of finishing super mario 3d world with Jacob or playing Pokemon battles with trinity in German class will always be in my heart. They brought me close to those I loved 💚💜 #nintendo #nintendoswitch #games

The Legend of Zelda: Link´s Awakening – Análisis (Switch) 17 de Junio de 1994. Yo tenía 12 años y recuerdo ese día como si fuese hoy. Empezaba el mundial de fútbol en Estados Unidos y pocas horas antes del pitido inicial mi padre llegó a casa con un regalo  El regalo  una GameBoy que a día de hoy todavía conservo. A partir de ese día cuando llegaban Navidades o cumpleaños mi catálogo de juegos de la consola portátil fue incrementando  pero entre todos ellos siempre tuve un título al que le tuve especial cariño. I beat Link’s Awakening last night! For the most part it was just as enjoyable as the original 1993 version that was my first 2D Zelda. Though I wouldn’t want it to return  the art style was charming and I did like it! Unfortunately  I do think more new features should have been added. Chamber Dungeons were a let down and figure collecting was pointless. The quality of life improvements were appreciated and I was grateful for more heart containers and seashells to hunt down and add to my total playtime. Most of the music was fantastic  with the tragic exception of Manbo’s Manbo which was hugely downgraded. Still I hope they release a soundtrack! $60 seems a bit unfair after everything is said and done  but I’m going to support the series I love best  regardless  in hopes of more remakes in the future. Gun Gun Pixies è un’esperienza che diverte per la sua leggerezza e fanservice. Non portando nulla di nuovo all’interno del settore più ecchi  si limita a elaborare la sua idea e a completarla il meglio possibile  utilizzando come maggior punti di forza un’art direction ben studiata e un ritmo di gameplay semplice ma efficace. Purtroppo la mancanza di uno vero spessore narrativo  un level design scomodo e una certa ripetitività evidente lo rendono un prodotto mirato quasi esclusivamente all’imperdibile appassionato della filosofia osé di PQube e Idea Factory/Compile Heart  perdendo l’occasione di poter sfruttare al meglio l’originalità dell’idea di base.La mia recensione per Tom's Hardware Game Division!⠀ -⠀ -⠀ -⠀ #gungunpixies #pqube #anime #fanservice #animegirl #pc #ps4 #playstation #nintendoswitch #sony #xbox #mcirosoft #gamingfolk #gaming #gamer #game #videogame #videogames #videogioco #videogiochi #nerd #geek #singleplayer #multiplayer #player #playing #play #gamereview #recensione

》Guten Morgen ihr Gamerchen《 So schnell geht es  da ist schon #Bergfest . 😂 Die liebe @apfelmotte_gaming hatte in ihrem aktuellen Post gefragt  was wir noch für Hobbies neben Videospielen haben und da wollte ich euch auch dran teilhaben lassen. Denn Brett- und Gemeinschaftsspiele sind auch ein großer Teil unseres Lebens. #dragonquestxiechidiuneraperduta  #dragonquest #nintendo #nintendoswitch #demo #squareenix #recensione #parliamone  Dragon Quest XI era uno dei giochi che più mi incuriosivano in questa stagione. Ammetto però che dopo ore giocate alla demo il mio interesse è lentamente scemato. Parliamo dei grandi punti di forza. Dragon Quest dal punto di vista estetico è bellissimo. Colorato  disegni che come sempre ammiccano alla serie di Dragon Ball e con una colonna sonora magistralmente diretta. Anche se sulla Switch in versione portatile perde molto  anzi sembra quasi che i luoghi più luminosi sembrano sgranati. Ma a mio avviso il problema principale è in gioco. I poligoni sono molto belli da vedere ma si muovono e interagiscono tra loro in un modo che non si vedeva da giochi della PS2. Il sistema di combattimento non è chissà quanto rivoluzionario e a volte risulta confuso e molto lento. Dalla demo non si ha modo di esplorare a pieno però tutto il compartimento GDR. In fine la trama sembra essere davvero molto avvincente ma agli inizi sembra troppo frettolosa sembrando a volte poco naturale. Spero che i difetti notati siano legati solo alla demo. Ma per i fan della saga forse può risultare un titolo imperdibile.

But something sparkly made Shin snap out of their drowsiness and almost fell into the water. What was that? The sun's reflection in the water? No. It was the golden sparkles of a chromatic Magikarp. The trainer did not hesitate to throw a pokeball at it. It was not hard to catch. Furi é um jogo de ação shoot 'em up  lançado em julho de 2016.Foi produzido e desenvolvido pela The Game Bakers (@gamebakers (produtora indie de outros títulos como Haven Squid Odyssey e Combo Crew).O furi está disponível para PS4 Nintendo switch Xbox One e Steam. O objetivo do jogo é eliminar todos os guardiões. Ele é um jogo de ação em ritmo acelerado com vários elementos ( hack and slash   twin-stick shoot 'up e "bullet hell"). As mecânicas deste game são variadas e com vários estilos podendo se tornar uma luta rápida e emocionante. Nestas mecânicas estão incluídos movimentos como desviar de balas  aparar ataques podendo atacar o chefe tanto com tiros e/ou com ataques corpo a corpo. Resumidamente (e sem spoilers) a história do jogo é a seguinte: Um homem misterioso passa sua existência recebendo tortura sem fim dentro de uma prisão altamente avançada  composta por dez ilhas flutuando em órbita acima da superfície de um planeta. No início do jogo  um homem enigmático usando um disfarce de coelho conhecido como The Voice liberta o Estranho  dá a ele uma espada e uma arma e o encoraja a lutar por sua liberdade. O Estranho deve navegar em cada área eliminando cada guardião que contém nela.A dificuldade alta (difícil) pode afastar jogadores mais inesperientes.  A trilha sonora de furi é sensacional  as batidas eletrônicas mixadas com efeitos de techno  pop e rock;trazendo mais emoção para esta aventura. Em síntese o furi é um excelente jogo para quem procura algo desafiador. Ele possui comandos rápidos e  com respostas precisas. Este jogo traz uma trilha sonora sensacional. O jogo possui múltiplos finais e um nível de dificuldade mais desafiador ao ser finalizado  que pode aumentar o fator replay para muitos jogadores e os aficionados por desafio. Queria agradecer a The Game Bakers por me ter dado uma cópia do game para fazer análise. Para aqueles que estão contando os dias para colocar as mãos no jogo  a Sony já iniciou o período de reserva do título.
